        <ontology:hasDescription>The total number of bed places (BPs) in tourist accommodations/year in the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is 4726. The regional (Region) share of total BPs/year is 15.60%. The number of agricultural holdings in the LAU is 74884. The nearest settlement with population over 100000 (km) is 60. In this region protected areas are not present.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


