        <ontology:hasDescription>The primary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 1.00%. The secondary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 42.40%. The tertiary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 56.60%. The primary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 3.10%. The secondary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 33.30%. The tertiary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 63.60%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
